articles.title: Jonas Vingegaard diagnosed with broken ribs and collarbone from Itzulia Basque Country crash - Global Cycling Network
articles.description: Visma-Lease a Bike announced that the two-time Tour de France champion is going to remain at the hospital as a precaution
articles.content:
Jonas Vingegaard (Visma-Lease a Bike) suffered several broken ribs and a broken collarbone from his crash on stage 4 of Itzulia Basque Country.
